00:32:17.000 --> 00:32:19.000
We started off with testing on the platform of, you know,

00:32:19.000 --> 00:32:20.000
having a model repo,

00:32:20.000 --> 00:32:23.000
because it was easier for us to test many different applications in one

00:32:23.000 --> 00:32:26.000
repo. So yeah, you can, when you looked in that primary file list,

00:32:26.000 --> 00:32:29.000
it'll auto complete all the things that we think look publishable.

00:32:29.000 --> 00:32:32.000
