00:32:34.000 --> 00:32:36.000
The other interesting thing about mono repos is like, we,

00:32:36.000 --> 00:32:39.000
we will look up the tree to find your requirements file.

00:32:39.000 --> 00:32:42.000
So if you have a requirements out TXT file on a Python project,

00:32:42.000 --> 00:32:45.000
let's say in route, and you don't have it in that sub directory,

00:32:46.000 --> 00:32:48.000
It'll eventually find it in that top one and allow you to,

00:32:48.000 --> 00:32:49.000
to publish from there.

00:32:51.000 --> 00:32:52.000
Awesome.

00:32:55.000 --> 00:32:57.000
